Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
MOAR VIEWS! - Tube Tycoon ►► http://bit.ly/1NNgKH9
JonTron is my OTP! - Asagao Academy ►► http://bit.ly/1WjkcMj
 
This game hits way too close to home. Living it up as a Youtuber isn't as easy as it seems and this Youtube simulator really emphasizes the frantic balancing act of the YouTuber's Lifestyle. But that isn't going to stop me from trying to become the number one Youtuber in the world! The struggle is real, but so is the determination. 

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
